12... gxf4 13. Bxf4 Bg7
{ We will play ... Nxe5 next. Our slightly weakened pawn structure will be compensated by active pieces. A sample line might go  14.Be2  Nxe5  15.O-O  Bg6  with ... Nd3 to come. We definitely have nothing to worry about here. }
