{ Since our position is intuitive to play whenever we get ... h4 in, this is the move that gives White the biggest hopes for something. White couldn't meet @@StartFEN@@r1b1k2r/ppp2ppp/3b4/4n3/8/2N3B1/PPP2PPP/R3KB1R b KQkq - 0 11@@EndFEN@@  11...h5  with  12.h4  due to  12...Bg4  as seen inthis variation, but here, ... Bg4 doesn't make much sense. }
