{ The best move, which has been White's choice in correspondence games only. OK, it also has been White's choice on Lichess three times, but accounts of all three players who chose  9.Nc3  are either blocked or closed. I wonder why?! OK, more seriously, nobody will ever play  9.Nc3  against you, but for the sake of completeness, here is my recommendation. }
