{ Smart, preparing Ba4. } 10... Bd7
{ Smart, declining Ba4.  10...c6?  11.Ba4  would be awful for us. } 11. Bxd7+
Qxd7 { Now, White has to move the King anyway. } 12. Kd1 Be7
{ But not  12...O-O-O?  13.Qxa7  which is very unclear. We should prepare castling queenside with ... a6 or just castle kingside. Full compensation for us! }
