{ Starting from this variation, we will take a look at White's rare tries on the 4th move. 4.Nxf7 is a dubious but interesting gambit in the @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.e4  e5  2.Nf3  Nf6  3.Nxe5  d6  4.Nxf7  variation. However, here, it loses on the spot. }
