{ Unstereotypical idea, but it just wins.  4...Kxf7??  5.Qh5+  would let White get the Knight back with one of the checks. }
5. Nxh8 Nc3+
{ The point. I find it poetic that White wanted to win our Queen using this trap by playing 4. Qe2, and in the end, our rival turned into prey and we were the hunter! }
