1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nxe5 Nxe4 4. Bd3
{ If White wants to speed up the kingside development, this is a smarter choice than  4.Bc4  . However, the d-pawn is blocked which indicates we shouldn't have issues getting a more pleasant game. }
4... d5 5. O-O Bd6
{ That's everything you need to know. Castle next and develop your pieces to the natural squares. }
