1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nxe5 Nxe4 4. Nf3
{ Retreating the Knight voluntarily is a concession. It was better to wait for something like ... d6 when we would be forced to lose a tempo later to play ... d6-d5. }
4... d5
