12... Nd5 13. exd6+ Kf8 14. Qe5 Bxd6 15. Qf5
{ It looks like White holds on, but... } 15... Qf6
{ White has to give up the Queen because  16.Qxf6  gxf6  opens up the g-file for the Rook. Black wins. }
