8. Nb5 { This looks scary, but we have a strong resource. } 8... Nxd5 9. exd5
Ne5
{ Just remember that our pieces want to be placed in the following manner:   • Knight to g6,   • Bishop to f6,   • Bishop to f5,  • Rook to e8.   • The Knight will be hit with ... a6 as well. }
