{ An important check, forcing more weaknesses on the kingside. } 8. g3 Qe7
{ Next is ... Nc6 followed by developing the light-squared Bishop @@StartBracket@@ideally to h3 or g4 - White has to move the Knight so it should be possible@@EndBracket@@ and castling queenside. }
