cxd5 8. O-O Nbc6
{ I'd like to develop the Knight before castling kingside. This gives us an additional option in the form of ... Bg4 before we castle.   Also,  8...O-O?!  allows  9.Ng5!  with decent attacking chances. }
9. Ne2 Qc7 { We keep the extra pawn and end up being much better. } *

