Rc8
{ An important move, developing with tempo and creating the threat of  11.--  11...Bxf3  Rxf3  Nxd4  Qxd4  Bc5  .  We also plan to drop the Bishop back to b8 without blocking the Rook. }
11. c3 Bb8
{ We threaten  12.--  12...Bxf3  Qxf3  Nxd4  , while ... Nd5 and ... Na5 are our positional ideas. }
