7. Nc3 { Initially, I thought this might be an issue but I think we are good. }
7... d4 { We grab space and free the d5-square for the Queen. } 8. Ne4 Qd5 9.
Nf2
{ 9.Nd6+?!  Bxd6  10.exd6  Kf8  is superb for Black.   9.c4  Qa5  10.c5  O-O-O  offers us excellent compensation. }
