O-O Nxc3 9. bxc3 Bxc3 10. Ba3 Bxa1 11. Qxa1 Be6 12. f4
{ In the theoretical section, I have mentioned that this is not a good option because it only weakens the White King and gives Black some additional possibilities. }
12... g6 13. Qb2 Rc8
{ 13...c6?!  planning  14.Qxb7  Qb6+  could be strongly considered. } 14. Qxb7
c5 { Black wants to castle into safety. } 15. Qxa7 Qc7
{ Erigaisi correctly evaluates that he has time to keep the strong pawn on c5. }
